### ====================================================================
### Ch09C 資料庫與 JPA 整合測試端點
### ====================================================================

### 1. 新增一位 D006 醫師 (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/doctors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctorId": "D006",
  "name": "黃國華",
  "department": "內科",
  "specialty": "糖尿病與內分泌新陳代謝"
}

### 2. 更新 D006 醫師的專長 (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D006
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "黃國華",
  "department": "內科",
  "specialty": "糖尿病、甲狀腺疾病與高血壓治療"
}

### 3. 刪除 D006 醫師 (DELETE)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D006

### 4. 取得所有病患清單
GET http://localhost:8080/api/patients

### 5. 取得特定病患 (TEST00001)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/patients/TEST00001

### 6. 取得總掛號數統計 (Part B)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/count

### 7. 依據看診日期篩選掛號
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments?date=2026-06-01

### 8. 依據醫生 ID 篩選掛號
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments?doctorId=D001